OPERANDS - [constants+variables]
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%% IMP %%
int ad ;
float kot, deta, alpha, beta ;
ad = 3200 ;
kot = 0.0056 ;
deta = alpha * beta / gamma + 3.2 * 2 / 5 ;

+,*, / - arthimetic operaters
3200 - interger constants
0.0056 - real conts
ad - integer variable
kot, deta - real variables
=  - assingment operater
